{moreoff lightred}Help for the {lightgreen}Read Topics Menu {lightmagenta}------------------

{lightgreen}An asterisk (*) next to the choice indicates that the topic has new
messages since you last read in this area.  The number in square brackets is
the number of messages in that topic.

{yellow}<0-9> Read Topic    {cyan}- Choose the topic or subject of interest and then
                      enter the number next to the topic to read ALL messages
                      in that topic thread.
{yellow}<A-J> Read Topic    {cyan}- Choose the topic or subject of interest and then
                      enter the letter next to the topic to read only NEW
                      messages in that topic thread.
{yellow}<P> Previous        {cyan}- This will take you back one page of choices.
{yellow}<N> Next            {cyan}- This will take you forward one page of choices.
{yellow}<X> Exit            {cyan}- Exit to the previous menu.

{lightcyan}Press {lightred blink}ENTER {lightcyan}to continue....{enter}
